Usage: report_ccopt_cell_halo_violations [-help] [-file <name>]
                                         [-num <integer>] [-summary] [-add_markers | -clear_markers ]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-add_markers                       # Adds any detected violations to the
                                   # violation browser. (bool, optional)
-clear_markers                     # Removes any markers added to the violation
                                   # browser by the
                                   # report_ccopt_cell_halo_violations command.
                                   # (bool, optional)
-file <name>                       # Save a copy of the contents of the report
                                   # to the specified file name (string, optional)
-num <integer>                     # Specifies the number of instances with a
                                   # cell halo violation to report by name
                                   # (int, optional)
-summary                           # Displays just the summary tables of cell
                                   # halo violations per clock tree
                                   # (bool, optional)